  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\">&minus;4<i>x</i>&sup2; + 28<i>x</i> + <i>c</i> = 0</p><p>In the given equation, <i>c</i> is a constant. The equation has exactly one solution. What is the value of <i>c</i>?</p>",
