  "rationale": "<p>A quadratic <i>a</i><i>x</i>&sup2; + <i>b</i><i>x</i> + <i>c</i> = 0 has exactly one solution when the discriminant is zero: <i>b</i>&sup2; &minus; 4<i>a</i><i>c</i> = 0. Here <i>a</i> = &minus;4, <i>b</i> = 28: 28&sup2; &minus; 4(&minus;4)<i>c</i> = 0, so 784 + 16<i>c</i> = 0, giving <i>c</i> = &minus;49.</p>",
